{"id":652599,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/【立此存照】何伟《中国是如何控制住新冠疫情的/","date":"2020-08-12T23:22:19Z","modified":"2020-08-13T02:28:49Z","title":"【立此存照】何伟《中国是如何控制住新冠疫情的？》中译部分删除并被大外宣利用","content":"<p>CDT编者按：作家何伟  ( Peter Hessler）在《纽约客》发表文章《中国是如何控制住新冠疫情的？》（How China Controlled the Coronavirus），第一时间被翻译成至少两种简体中文版在中文社交媒体上传播。细心的网友发现，和英文原文相比，译文不约而同删除了提到“中国在初期掩盖疫情”以及中国对香港和新疆政策的一段话（译者有标注）。除此之外，中共大外宣官媒CGTN（中国国际电视台）迫不及待地利用何伟的文章扬中抑美。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>原文与译文对照：</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652603\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报-300x255.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报-300x255.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报-1024x872.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报-768x654.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报-1536x1307.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报-1080x919.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/纽约时报.png 1706w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652601\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦-204x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"734\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦-204x300.jpg 204w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦-698x1024.jpg 698w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦-768x1127.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦-1047x1536.jpg 1047w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦-1080x1585.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/复旦.jpg 1125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652602\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/樊百乐2-300x138.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"230\" srcset=\"http